name: Black Google in LCARS terminal (adlc)
description:
This is a black Google in LCARS 24th century terminal.
works with all Google (not gmail!)

It has been splited in two part. 
Part II of this style can be found here: http://userstyles.org/styles/36828

As usual, bugs can be reported here or to the Vulcan Science Academy, Shikar Vulcan UFP.
Enjoy !
